#Covers File handling in c++ 

STEP 1:  Start the program.

STEP 2:  Declare the variables.

STEP 3:  Read the file name.

STEP 4:  open the file to write the contents(welcome to globaledge).

STEP6:   write the file contents as uppercase.

STEP7:   Close the file.

STEP7:   Now,open the file to read the contents and display contents.

STEP 8:  Stop the program. 
